    public class KlekotaRothFingerprinter
extends SubstructureFingerprinter
    SMARTS based substructure fingerprint based on Chemical substructures that enrich for biological activity [Klekota, Justin and Roth, Frederick P., Chemical substructures that enrich for biological activity, Bioinformatics, 2008, 24:2518-2525, doi:10.1093/bioinformatics/btn479]. Presence of 4860 substructures
